    "v3": "Jesus wants us to be loving, helping when we may. We will try to be kindhearted, merciful each day.",
    "v4": "&quot;Blessed are the pure in heart,&quot; thus the Savior taught. Clean in mind, in soul, in body, pure in every thought.",
    "v5": "When we find our friends are angry, we will to them say, &quot;Jesus wants you to be loving, each and every day.&quot;"
  },
